DTSTART:20260915T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:Conference Details:  The Ken Kennedy Institute at Rice Universi
	ty invites you to the 5th annual AI in Health Conference!Join in on discus
	sions with researchers\, clinicians\, and engineers utilizing artificial i
	ntelligence to influence real-world health outcomes and improve patient ca
	re.&#160\;Save the Dates: September 15-17\, 2026Location:  BioScience Rese
	arch Collaborative (BRC)  Rice University  6500 Main St\, Houston\, TX 770
	30  Houston\, TXWebsite: Visit https://kenkennedy.rice.edu/aihealthconfere
	nce (https://kenkennedy.rice.edu/aihealthconference) for program updatesPa
